snippet.title: Best phones
snippet.description: Looking for phones? CNET's reviews of the best phones include photos, video, and user reviews.

snippet.title: Watch a woman get a 3D-printed skull
snippet.description: When a Dutch woman with a rare condition needed a new skull, surgeons 3D-printed one for her and put it on her brain like a cap.

snippet.title: Set up an animated talking skull
snippet.description: Spice up your Halloween decorations with scary props and sound effects. CNET's Donald Bell shows you how to connect and operate an interactive talking skull.

snippet.title: Cinemagram for Android
snippet.description: If you just want to make some cinemagraphs, then this app is great at it. However, it does have some performance issues that could make sharing difficult.

snippet.title: Asus Memo Pad ME172V
snippet.description: The Asus Memo Pad ME172V won't set you back a ton, but with much better choices only $50 away, you should simply pay more now and regret less later.

snippet.title: Uniface mask: Glue on some bionic skin, feel fabulous
snippet.description: Could getting a new face be as easy as ordering a mask online? One woman's statement on beauty has giant anime eyes, long lashes, and a high nose bridge to help you meet today's standards.

snippet.title: Anonymous' 'Million Mask March' goes global
snippet.description: With 450 cities on the roster, the hacking collective takes its online protests to the streets.

snippet.title: Petman robot rocks gas mask, chemical suit
snippet.description: You wouldn't want to meet this camouflaged humanoid in a dark alley. For the time being, it's tethered to a treadmill.

snippet.title: Antenna implanted in cyborg's skull gets Wi-Fi, color as sound
snippet.description: Artist and cyborg advocate Neil Harbisson has an "eyeborg," a device implanted in his skull that lets him hear colors. Friends can even use an app to beam images to his brain. Crave's Michael Franco talks with him about cyborg advocacy, turning music into clothing, and life with a new sense you can never shut off.

snippet.title: AwoX StriimLight B-10
snippet.description: The StriimLight B-10 and StriimLight Wi-Fi are LEDs with integrated speakers that let you adjust music volume and bulb brightness from your couch.
